 those\nin which the inner apparent horizon collapses to zero radius early in their\nevolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2020 18:46:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Apr 2020 16:46:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-20"}
