eld-out log-likelihood across all datasets. Therefore, we recommend\nusing a simple prior for the latent variable non-autoregressive model when fast\ngeneration speed is desired.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2020 20:13:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
