ituations such as systems of SPDEs with\nlinearizations only generating a strongly continuous semigroup. This provides a\nrelevant generalization as these systems are prevalent in many applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2020 20:16:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 30 Oct 2021 13:08:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-20"}
